# Local AI / contributor context index

**Do not delete this file.** It is the navigation map for humans and agents; extend it when behavior or layout changes.

**Tracked in git** (not ignored) so clones keep the map. Edit anchors if line numbers drift.

---

## Quick navigation

| Area | Primary files |
|------|----------------|
| HTTP API + JSON store | `server.js` |
| HTML shell + ids | `index.html` |
| Events, auth, mutations | `js/main.js` |
| Dashboard + log + scheduled DOM | `js/render.js` |
| Presets, points, quick bar | `js/presets.js` |
| Shared state | `js/state.js` |
| Styles (split by feature) | `css/chore-tracker-*.css` |

---

`server.js` — API + persistence + import/export/store normalization.
- `135` `normalizeEntry(row)` — entry shape, `choreId`, `locationIds`.
- `163` `normalizeChorePreset(row)` — validates title/points/color/scoringMode.
- `178` `normalizeChorePresets(arr)` — array normalization for presets.
- `188` `normalizeQuickChoreIds(ids, presets)` — validates quick bar ids against presets.
- `291` `normalizeStore(raw)` — canonicalizes store object read from disk (`discordWebhook`, `discordReminderSentAt`).
- `451` `app.get('/api/entries', ...)` — list entries + `discordWebhook` for settings UI.
- Discord: `POST /api/discord-webhook/test`, `POST /api/discord-webhook/remind-now`; background timer sends overdue scheduled-chore reminders per `discordReminderSentAt`.
- `469`–`542` scheduled chore routes; `PUT /api/scheduled-chores/:id` supports title/interval/**startsOn** updates; `542` `POST .../complete` writes completion entry.
- `588` `app.put('/api/settings', ...)` — settings write (people/presets/quick ids/locations).
- `657` `app.post('/api/import', ...)` — import handler (replace/merge modes).
- `634` `app.get('/api/export', ...)` — export.
- `768` `app.post('/api/entries', ...)` — add entry (supports `choreId`, locations).
- `830` `app.put('/api/entries/:id', ...)` — update entry.

`index.html` — app shell, dialogs, script bootstrap.
- Settings: **Discord reminders** (`#discordWebhookEnabled`, `#discordWebhookUrl`, `#discordReminderInterval`, test / post-now buttons).
- `62`–`74` **analytics filters** `#analyticsPersonFilter`, `#analyticsLocationFilter`, hint `#analyticsFilterHint`; then `analytics-stats-row` / `statsGrid`, `statsGridPoints`.
- `76`–`94` `section-pair`: contributions (`barsArea`, `barsAreaPoints`) + heatmap `taskHeatmap`.
- `114`–`145` log form: `inChore`, `#scheduledLogSuggestionsWrap` / `#scheduledLogSuggestions` (due soon / overdue, preset title match), `inLocations`, quick log.
- `147`+ `log-mom-row`: **log filter** `#logSearch`, `#logList`, `momGrid`, `momGridPoints`.
- (approx.) `<script type="module" src="/js/chore-tracker.js">` at end of body.

`js/chore-tracker.js` — thin entrypoint → `main.js`.

`js/main.js` — event wiring, auth/bootstrap, mutations, import/export UI flows.
- `205` `load()` — fetch entries/settings, populate state.
- `295` `addEntry()` — main add flow; semicolon payload, posts `/api/entries`.
- `fillChoreFromPreset(presetId)` — sets `#inChore` + per-location locations (shared with quick log).
- `quickLogChore(presetId)` — `fillChoreFromPreset` then `addEntry()`.
- `initScheduledLogSuggestions()` — delegated click on `#scheduledLogSuggestions` → fill + focus chore field.
- `saveScheduledStartDate(id, domKey)` — updates scheduled chore `startsOn` from manage-list date input.
- `524` `startApp()` — init date field, load, pick month, `render()`.
- `534` `bootstrap()` — session check + app/login visibility.
- `#monthSelect` → `switchMonth` (clears log search only).
- `#analyticsPersonFilter` / `#analyticsLocationFilter` `change` → `app.analyticsPersonFilter` / `app.analyticsLocationFilter`, `render()`.
- `#logSearch` `input` → `app.logSearchQuery`, `render()`.
- export/import handlers (`/api/export`, `/api/import`).
- `initQuickChores()`; `initScheduledLogSuggestions()`; chore suggest init nearby.

`js/presets.js` — chore presets + quick log editor + payload resolution.
- `6` `syncChoreDatalists()` — syncs edit dialog datalist.
- `16` `entryChorePoints(e)` — points from preset + per_location × locations.
- `presetMatchingScheduledTitle(title)` — preset match for scheduled log suggestions (exact, then small Levenshtein budget).
- `27` `resolveChorePayloadRows(raw)` — splits `;` and resolves preset ids.
- `43` `saveChorePresetsAndQuick()` — persists settings to `/api/settings`.
- preset/quick editors + `renderQuickChores`.

`js/chore-input-suggest.js` — custom suggestion list for `#inChore`.
- `initChoreInputSuggest()` — keyboard/mouse + segment-aware filtering.

`js/render.js` — render pipeline for dashboard/log/scheduled views.
- `14` `entryMatchesAnalyticsFilters` / `entriesForAnalyticsMonth` — person + location filters for stats/bars/heatmap/MoM (location = entry `locationIds` includes selected name).
- `entryMatchesLogSearch` — log-only text filter (whitespace AND tokens).
- `countsByPerson` / `pointsByPerson` / `taskCountsByDay` — use `entriesForAnalyticsMonth`.
- `fullRender()` — analytics filters, dual stat grids, bars, heatmap, log list, **scheduled log suggestion buttons** (`scheduledStatus` overdue/today/soon + `presetMatchingScheduledTitle`), dual MoM, scheduled dashboard.
- `switchMonth` — sets `app.currentMonth`, clears `app.logSearchQuery`, `render()`.
- `setRenderRenderer(fullRender)` registration.

`js/state.js` — shared mutable app state (`app.entries`, `app.currentMonth`, `app.logSearchQuery`, **`app.analyticsPersonFilter`**, **`app.analyticsLocationFilter`**, …).

`js/render-registry.js` — indirection to avoid import cycles.

`js/scheduled-logic.js` — `scheduledStatus(s)` (overdue / today / soon ≤3 days / later); `intervalLabel`.

`js/utils/date.js` — date helpers and month keys.

`js/api-fetch.js` — fetch wrapper with auth redirect behavior.

`css/chore-tracker-base.css` — reset/theme/shell, top bar, settings dialog, toast.
- `:root` includes `--layout-max-width` (820px; widens at `1100px` / `1440px`).
- `.wrap` uses `var(--layout-max-width)`.

`css/chore-tracker-dashboard.css` — **`.analytics-filters`**, stats, sections, heatmap, bars, MoM, desktop side-by-side rows.

`css/chore-tracker-forms.css` — log form, edit dialog, **`.log-filter-row` / `.log-search-input`**, `.log-list` height (taller at `1100px` + `log-mom-row`).

`css/chore-tracker-scheduled.css` — scheduled dashboard + dialogs + start-date editor (`.scheduled-start-edit`) + **`.scheduled-log-suggestions`** / `.scheduled-suggest-btn`.

`css/chore-tracker-auth.css` — login screen visibility and card.

`css/chore-tracker-extras.css` — chore suggest, preset editors, `#inLocations`, `.log-chore-points`.

`data/chores.json` — persisted store (`entries`, `people`, `chorePresets`, `quickChoreIds`, `locations`, `scheduledChores`, …).

---

## Analytics filters (client-only)

- State: `app.analyticsPersonFilter` (empty = all), `app.analyticsLocationFilter` (empty = all). Not cleared on month change.
- UI: `#analyticsPersonFilter`, `#analyticsLocationFilter`, `#analyticsFilterHint` above the stat grids.
- Scope: task + points stats, contribution bars, daily heatmap, month-over-month (current vs previous month both use the same filters). **Does not** change the activity log (`#logList`); use log search there.
- Location: an entry matches only if `locationIds` includes the selected location (entries with no locations excluded when a location is selected).

## Log search / filter (client-only)

- State: `app.logSearchQuery` (string). Cleared when the month dropdown changes (`switchMonth`).
- UI: `#logSearch` under “Log for …”; styles in `chore-tracker-forms.css`.
- Matching: `entryMatchesLogSearch` — whitespace tokens AND; haystack = date, chore, person, locations, points. Only affects `#logList`.

## Scheduled log suggestions (client-only)

- Shown when a scheduled chore is **overdue**, **due today**, or **due within 3 days** (`scheduledStatus` `soon`), and its **title matches a chore preset** (exact case-insensitive, or close fuzzy match via `presetMatchingScheduledTitle` — e.g. “Wipe …” vs “Wiped …”).
- Renders under “Log a chore”, above Quick log. Tap fills `#inChore` (and per-location selects like quick log); user picks person/date and **Add**. Does **not** call scheduled “complete” API — use Scheduled dashboard **Mark done** to reset the timer.

---

## Feature map (short)

- Auth/session: login/logout + cookie session guard.
- Chore logging: date/person/chore; semicolon multi-preset; locations for `per_location` presets.
- Quick log: auto-fills locations for per-location presets when none selected.
- Custom chore suggestions.
- Presets + quick bar: CRUD, scoring modes, persist via `/api/settings`.
- Log edit/delete; **log text filter** (current month list only).
- Scheduled chores: due states, complete/remove, editable **start date**, plus log-form suggestions when due + preset title match.
- Analytics: task-count and preset-points metrics; heatmap; **person + location filters** (stats/bars/heatmap/MoM); import/export; theme + PWA.

## Future ideas (implementation-oriented)

- History/audit metadata on entries.
- Soft delete/archive presets.
- Fuzzy search for multi-segment chore input.
- Optional reminders for scheduled chores.
- Tests: API import merge + client resolver/scheduled logic.
- Backup snapshots before import.
